<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM4.8">
<l>piṟaiyēṟu caṭaiyāṉum piramaṉu mintiraṉu</l>
<l>muṟaiyāya peruvēḷvik kuṟaimuṭippāṉ maṟaiyāṉāṉ</l>
<l>veṟiyārtaṇ cōlait tiruvēṅ kaṭamalaimēl</l>
<l>neṟiyāyk kiṭakkum nilaiyuṭaiyē ṉāvēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I shall possess the state of lying as a path upon the mountain of the sacred Veṅkaṭa</l>
<l>with cool, fragrance-filled flower gardens</l>
<l>of Him who is the Vedas, Him who ends [their] grievances [as]</l>
<l rend="indent">he with matted-locks on which the crescent moon stands,</l>
<l rend="indent">Brahmā and Indra [perform] big yajnas in the [proper] manner.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
